	<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,5,0,5">Lazy numbering can be accomplished by prefixing items with <TextBlock xml:space="preserve" TextWrapping="Wrap" FontFamily="Courier New">#.</TextBlock>:</TextBlock>
	<Grid Margin="0,5,0,5">
		<Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
			<ColumnDefinition Width="Auto" />
			<ColumnDefinition Width="*" />
		</Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
		<Grid.RowDefinitions>
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto" />
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto" />
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto" />
		</Grid.RowDefinitions>
		<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Column="0" Grid.Row="0" Margin="0,0,5,0">1.</TextBlock>
		<StackPanel Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="0">
			<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">Bird</TextBlock>
		</StackPanel>
		<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Column="0" Grid.Row="1" Margin="0,0,5,0">2.</TextBlock>
		<StackPanel Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="1">
			<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">McHale</TextBlock>
		</StackPanel>
		<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Column="0" Grid.Row="2" Margin="0,0,5,0">3.</TextBlock>
		<StackPanel Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="2">
			<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">Parish</TextBlock>
		</StackPanel>
	</Grid>
	<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,5,0,5">To make lists look nice, you can wrap items with hanging indents:</TextBlock>
	<Grid Margin="0,5,0,5">
		<Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
			<ColumnDefinition Width="Auto" />
			<ColumnDefinition Width="*" />
		</Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
		<Grid.RowDefinitions>
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto" />
			<RowDefinition Height="Auto" />
		</Grid.RowDefinitions>
		<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Column="0" Grid.Row="0" Margin="0,0,5,0">1.</TextBlock>
		<StackPanel Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="0">
			<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aliquam hendrerit mi posuere lectus. Vestibulum enim wisi, viverra nec, fringilla in, laoreet vitae, risus.</TextBlock>
		</StackPanel>
		<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Grid.Column="0" Grid.Row="1" Margin="0,0,5,0">2.</TextBlock>
		<StackPanel Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="1">
			<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap">Donec sit amet nisl. Aliquam semper ipsum sit amet velit. Suspendisse id sem consectetuer libero luctus adipiscing.</TextBlock>
		</StackPanel>
	</Grid>
	<TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Margin="0,5,0,5">But if you want to be lazy, you don’t have to:</TextBlock>
